(17, 'Виртуальный тур', 'Посетите наш заповедник с помощью виртуального тура', '', '<p>This is Photoshop\'s version of Lorem Ipsum. Proin gravida nibh vel velit auctor aliquet. Aenean sollicitudin, lorem quis bibendum auctor, nisi elit consequat ipsum, nec sagittis sem nibh id elit. Duis sed odio sit amet nibh vulputate cursus a sit amet maurisllam ac urna eu felis dapibus condimentum sit amet a augue. Sed non neque elit. Sed ut imperdiet nisi. Proin condimentum fermentum nunc</p>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"virtualtour\"><img title=\"tour\" src=\"/upload/Image/tour.jpg\" alt=\"tour\" width=\"1000\" height=\"534\" /></div>', '/ru/virtual-tour/6', '', 'pages-thumb-17.png', 16, 17, 0, 0, 2, '2015-04-09 01:24:30', 'ru', 2),
